videos.headline: Wisconsin 68-yard run, Badgers keep possesion after fumble

videos.description: Badgers quarterback Alex Hornibrook throws a 24-yard touchdown pass to Jazz Peavy as Wisconsin extends their lead to 10-0 over Ohio State.
videos.headline: Badgers' Hornibrook tosses 24-yard TD

videos.headline: Marcus Baugh's acrobatic 29-yard catch gives Buckeyes first down

videos.headline: A. Hornibrook pass,to T. Fumagalli for 30 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: J.T. Barrett's one-yard touchdown run brings Ohio State closer to Wisconsin at 16-13.
videos.headline: Barrett's runs in for one-yard score

videos.description: J.T. Barrett runs to the outside, cruising eight yards to the end zone for the touchdown as the Buckeyes take a 20-16 lead over Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Barrett, OSU rally, force OT at Wisconsin

videos.description: Wisconsin FB Austin Ramesh rushes up the middle, powers through a defender and scores a touchdown as the Badgers reclaim the lead over Ohio State 23-20.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Ramesh powers up the middle for TD
Ohio State ties game with 31-yard FG

videos.description: Tied at 23 in overtime, J.T. Barrett connects with Noah Brown for a seven-yard touchdown to give Ohio State the lead.
videos.headline: Barrett finds Brown for game-winning TD in OT

videos.description: Down 16-6 at halftime, J.T. Barrett runs in for two scores and in overtime he connects with Noah Brown for a 7-yard touchdown with the Buckeyes prevailing over Wisconsin for a 30-23 victory.
videos.headline: Barrett, OSU erase deficit, defeat Wisconsin in OT
